title: Brihappen Military Tank Building Blocks Sets for Adult, WW2 German IV Heavy Tank Collection Model Construction Toys, for Adult Kids Boy Military Enthusiasts（1419 Pcs
features: 【Military Tanks Building Set】This military tank consists of 1419 pieces of high quality blocks, the whole armed tank model measures 10.83 (L) * 4.72 (W) * 4.33 (H) inches. In addition, the package includes a bagged accessory kit and detailed colourful instructions to help you complete the assembly easily.

【Realistic Tank Model】With rich structure and unique design, the military tank model is a cool World War II toy model. The turret can be rotated 360°, the gun barrel can be lifted and the hatch can be opened. The layout inside the hatch highly reproduces the cabin view of a real tank. Every detail is carefully designed, so its appearance is very realistic.

【Cool Military Collectibles for Home Office】Tank block model is an impressive and cool and realistic looking military style collectible that is not easy to deform or fade no matter how long you collect it. Also great for perfect decorations in your room or office.

【Military-themed Educational Building Block Toys】The military tank building block toy is a military themed educational toy and a journey of discovery looking back at World War II. In the process of building, you can also experience the fun brought by the blocks, temporarily forgetting your worries and releasing stress. It can improve your hands-on ability, thinking ability, concentration, memory, imagination and creativity.

【Ideal Gifts】Whether it's birthday, Christmas, Thanksgiving, anniversary, Father's Day, Valentine's Day, wedding or New Year's celebration, this military tank block kit is a beautiful gift for any occasion. It's perfect for boys, men, adults, military enthusiasts and tank collectors ages 14 and up.
